<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB07824</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT PROVIDING FOR THE MODERNIZATION OF THE PHILIPPINE NATIONAL POLICE, APPROPRIATING FUNDS THEREFOR, AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Creates a two part modernization program: 1.) Infrastructure Development and Facilities Upgrading; and 2.) Equipment Upgrading and Acquisition Planning; Strengthens the PNP procurement system and procedures.  </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ALIAS NAME : “PNP Modernization Act of 2017.” </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ACOP, ROMEO M., ESPINO, AMADO JR. T., BATAOIL, LEOPOLDO N.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2018-05-30</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Del Mar (000 2018-08-01)</td><td>2. Olivarez (000 2018-08-14)</td><tr><td>3. Tambunting (000 2018-08-15)</td><td>4. Nieto (000 2018-11-29)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON PUBLIC ORDER AND SAFETY ON 2018-07-30</td></tr></table>